org.wicketstuff.html5.media.webvtt

Class VttCue

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wicketstuff.html5.media.webvtt.VttCue

  • public class VttCue
extends Object
    A cue block containing the translations

    Base on the browser cues can be styled with CSS. So you only have to include a CSS file into the HTML page the video is embedded.

    Further information:
    http://tiffanybbrown.com/2013/12/14/subtitles-and-captions-with-webvtt/
    Author:
    Tobias Soloschenko
